{"tid":1502951,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"「不推文回覆」呢個功能可唔可以變做一粒掣放喺「發表」側邊","createTime":"2019-08-24T18:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T04:05:57.000Z","uid":23094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cda3cfdadbbed9adbfc86d779f0b76c2513eee0e","tid":1502951,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:41:18.000Z","msg":"我發現好多人都唔記得用不推文回覆<br />\n結果就推郁咗個Post<br />\n<br />\n如果個掣放喺平時出Post掣側邊<br />\n效果應該會好好多<br />\n<br />\n類似咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e8tHxV7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe8tHxV7.png&h=5d3e8615&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f0adefcd1fa34887997cbf4aba9b965c38c82e3","tid":1502951,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:42:33.000Z","msg":"同埋唔好limit 1 分鐘得唔得。。"},{"pid":"b7618d2d432683fd4eeab06cff61e4b95e6d54b1","tid":1502951,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:44:08.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"47b33f16bcf44255de83ea7029f067911117ad94","tid":1502951,"uid":301648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"我P牌都同意，雖然而今係咪都冇得推，但登記頭幾日重推到，重有少少記憶。<br />\n<br />\n不推文變另一個「發表」掣會解決兩個問題：<br />\n1. 不推文功能喺手機版同電腦版唔同樣，令人用慣電腦喺手機搵唔到個功能，或者用慣手機喺電腦搵唔到<br />\n2. 如果唔知有呢個功能存在，根本就睇唔到粒掣"}]}